OL,3,CMohamud Hassan: 'No evidence' that
OL,4,Cofficers' actions contributed to death
OL,6,FAn investigation has found the actions
OL,7,Fof police did not contribute to the
OL,8,Fdeath of a man who had been in custody
OL,9,Fin Cardiff.
OL,11,FMohamud Hassan, 24, died at a flat on
OL,12,FNewport Road in January 2021 after
OL,13,Fbeing released by officers.
OL,15,FHe had been arrested the previous
OL,16,Fnight on suspicion of an alleged
OL,17,Fbreach of the peace.
