OL,3,CMohamud Hassan: 'No evidence' that
OL,4,Cofficers' actions contributed to death
OL,6,FAn Independent Office for Police
OL,7,FConduct (IOPC) investigation into the
OL,8,Factions of South Wales Police Officers
OL,9,Fconcluded he was not treated less
OL,10,Ffavourably because of his race but was
OL,11,Fshown a lack of respect by some
OL,12,Fofficers.
OL,14,FAt an inquest held in Pontypridd, the
OL,15,Fjury today (2 May) returned on open
OL,16,Foutcome for Mr Hassan's cause of
OL,17,Fdeath. The cause of death was given as
OL,18,Funascertained.
