OL,3,CMohamud Hassan: 'No evidence' that
OL,4,Cofficers' actions contributed to death
OL,6,FMr Hassan was released the morning
OL,7,Fafter his arrest. At 10.22pm that day,
OL,8,Fa family member made an emergency call
OL,9,Fstating that he had been found
OL,10,Funresponsive.
OL,12,FAt 10.29pm, paramedics arrived at the
OL,13,Fproperty and, soon after, confirmed
OL,14,Fthat Mr Hassan had died.
OL,16,FA post-mortem examination showed that
OL,17,Fthere was no physical injury sustained
OL,18,Fby Mr Hassan to explain a cause of
OL,19,Fdeath.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/11
