OL,3,CMohamud Hassan: 'No evidence' that
OL,4,Cofficers' actions contributed to death
OL,6,FThe post-mortem evidence also stated
OL,7,Fthat there was no indication of the
OL,8,Fuse of a Taser, or of weapons such as
OL,9,Fbatons.
OL,11,FThe IOPC investigation found that
OL,12,Fthere was evidence that Mr Hassan may
OL,13,Fhave felt discriminated against and
OL,14,Fthat he voiced that belief to officers
OL,15,Fwhile he was in custody.
