OL,3,CMohamud Hassan: 'No evidence' that
OL,4,Cofficers' actions contributed to death
OL,6,FAfter scrutinising bodycam footage,
OL,7,Faudio recordings, and taking witness
OL,8,Fstatements, investigators also found
OL,9,Fthat evidence did not support the
OL,10,Fassertion that Mr Hassan was treated
OL,11,Fless favourably by officers because of
OL,12,Fhis race, or that he had been
OL,13,Fassaulted by officers.
OL,15,FHowever, the watchdog did determine
OL,16,Fthat there was an overall lack of
OL,17,Frespect and care in the way some
OL,18,Fofficers treated Mr Hassan during his
OL,19,Farrest, transport and detention.
