OL,3,CMohamud Hassan: 'No evidence' that
OL,4,Cofficers' actions contributed to death
OL,6,FHe continued: "This was a complex
OL,7,Finvestigation, examining police
OL,8,Fcontact over an extended period. We
OL,9,Freviewed a large amount of evidence
OL,10,Fincluding detailed accounts from a
OL,11,Fsignificant number of officers
OL,12,Finvolved, either directly or
OL,13,Findirectly, with Mr Hassan, accounts
OL,14,Ffrom family members, police body worn
OL,15,Fvideo, CCTV footage, photographs,
OL,16,Fpolice radio transmissions and call
OL,17,Flogs. Investigators examined the
OL,18,Fpolice cell in which Mr Hassan was
OL,19,Fdetained and visited the property on
OL,20,FNewport Road, to view the scene of his
OL,21,Farrest and secure relevant evidence.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/11
