OL,3,CMohamud Hassan: 'No evidence' that
OL,4,Cofficers' actions contributed to death
OL,6,F"Whilst we identified some areas of
OL,7,Flearning for South Wales Police and
OL,8,Ffor individuals arising from the
OL,9,Fevents, and a case to answer for one
OL,10,Fofficer for use of force, we found no
OL,11,Fevidence that the actions of police
OL,12,Fofficers had contributed to Mr
OL,13,FHassan's sad death.
OL,15,F"After our investigation was
OL,16,Fcompleted, we provided Mr Hassan's
OL,17,Ffamily with the detail of our findings
OL,18,Fand submitted our report to the
OL,19,Fcoroner to assist with the inquest."
