OL,3,CMohamud Hassan: 'No evidence' that
OL,4,Cofficers' actions contributed to death
OL,6,FIn reaction to the findings, South
OL,7,FWales Police Assistant Chief Constable
OL,8,FJoanna Maal said: "We can only imagine
OL,9,Fhow difficult this period of time has
OL,10,Fbeen for Mohamud Hassan's family and
OL,11,Fthe pain and grief that they have
OL,12,Fendured since his death.
OL,14,F"This case has been the subject of
OL,15,Fmuch independent and public scrutiny.
OL,16,FNow that the facts have been published
OL,17,Fand heard during the inquest
OL,18,Fproceedings we hope that answers have
OL,19,Fbeen provided to the many questions
OL,20,Fwhich have been raised."
